}}</ref>，其中鈣離子浓度通常比鎂稀至少一千倍。

==性質==
EGTA与鈣離子結合的[[酸解離常數|pKa]]值為11.00；但是在pH=7，EGTA被质子化，对螯合的贡献被削弱，pKa值變為6.91。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Ning Qin, Riccardo Olcese, Michael Bransby, Tony Lin, and Lutz Birnbaumer | title = Ca<sup>2+</sup>-induced inhibition of the cardiac Ca<sup>2+</sup> channel depends on calmodulin | journal = [[PNAS|PNAS]] | volume = 96 | issue = 5 | pages = 2435–2438 | url = http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/full/96/5/2435 | accessdate = 2007-10-22 | pmid = 10051660 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.96.5.2435 | pmc = 26802 | date = March 1999 | archive-date = 2008-05-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080511073046/http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/full/96/5/2435 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==用途==
EGTA可以用於動物的[[鈰|鈰]]中毒治療，與從[[磷铈镧矿|磷铈镧矿]]中分離出[[釷|釷]]。EGTA亦用于制备[[洗脱|洗脱]]缓冲液，在稱為“{{link-en|串聯親和純化|Tandem affinity purification}}”（TAP）的蛋白質純化技术中使用，其中“重組融合蛋白”（Fusion protein）与[[钙调蛋白|钙调蛋白]]结合，并被EGTA洗脱出来。

EGTA也經常在牙科[[根管治療|根管治療]]中用到，去除玷污層。

